    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <div class='blurb'>
          <h1>Stories are like...</h1>
          <p>A ball of yarn. Have fun weaving them with others,<br> form tight-knit friendships, and spin your story to the world!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_position">
          <a href="/rooms/main"><button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg raised get_started" type="button">Get Started</button></a>
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg raised learn_more" type="button">Learn More</button>
        </div>  
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="responsive-layer">
      <div class='container-fluid'>
        <div class="row">
          <div class='col-md-4'>
            <div class="panel-body">
              <div id="img1" ></div>
              <h4>Spool</h4>
              <p>Got a story in you? Choose any genre you like and we’ll find you a creative space with others interested in the same genre. </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-4'>
            <div class="panel-body">
              <div id="img2"></div>
              <h4>Weave</h4>
              <p>Once everyone is in, someone is chosen at random to start and each person takes turns adding to the current story. You can skip a turn if you like. The story ends after a certain number of turns which you decide when you spool.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-4'>
            <div class="panel-body">
              <div id="img3"></div>
              <h4>Spin</h4>
              <p>You and your (new) friends have just weaved a captivating story? Spin it to the world through Facebook or Google+!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  
